definition: to get rid of/to remove/to exclude/to eliminate/to wipe out/to divide/except/not including

to go/to go to (a place)/(of a time etc) last/just passed/to send/to remove/to get rid of/to reduce/to be apart from in space or time/to die (euphemism)/to play (a part)/(when used either before or after a verb) to go in order to do sth/(after a verb of motion indicates movement away from the speaker)/(used after certain verbs to indicate detachment or separation)

sentences.english: You'll never get the bacon grease off the plates if you don't use detergent.
sentences.chinese: 如果你不使用去垢剂你永远不能除去熏猪肉的油脂。

sentences.english: Commercial scale test of selective precipitation method for Mo removal from tungstate solution;
sentences.chinese: 研究了用硫酸铜沉淀法除去粗钨酸钠溶液中钼的方法。

sentences.english: Fear keeps us from surrendering, but love casts out all fear.
sentences.chinese: 恐惧阻碍我们降服，但爱能除去一切恐惧。

sentences.english: Her name was dropped from the list.
sentences.chinese: 她的名字已从名单上除去了。

sentences.english: Content that is hidden to the user is not removed from the page, but is obscured.
sentences.chinese: 对用户隐藏的信息并没有从页面上除去，而是隐藏了。

sentences.english: A hydrocyclone device that removes large drill solids from the whole mud system.
sentences.chinese: 一种从整个泥浆系统中除去大钻屑的水力旋流装置。

sentences.english: Is it possible to make the dialog draggable even after removing the titlebar?
sentences.chinese: 这可能使对话即使除去标题栏拖动？

sentences.english: He is removing weeds with a harrow in the rice field.
sentences.chinese: 他正在用耥耙给稻田除去杂草。

sentences.english: Removal of some system test defects earlier in the product cycle.
sentences.chinese: 在产品周期较早期除去一些系统测试缺陷。

sentences.english: To remove the foreleg, cut through the hide and tendons AT the joint closest to the foot.
sentences.chinese: 除去前腿时要通过皮和筋在脚的关节处切下去。

sentences.english: When the barge reached the shrine, acolytes removed the pall.
sentences.chinese: 当驳船抵达圣地时，辅祭除去了柩衣。

sentences.english: The masking patterns and the spacers are removed using the filler plugs as a hard mask.
sentences.chinese: 利用填料塞作为硬掩模来除去掩模图案和隔离层。

sentences.english: How on eliminate face " fabaceous beans " , make the skin white fair-skinned ?
sentences.chinese: 怎么除去脸上的“豆豆”，让皮肤白皙？

sentences.english: All almonds undergo mandatory pasteurization to remove poison and bacteria -- which has stirred up food controversy since 2007.
sentences.chinese: 所有的杏仁都要经过消毒以除去其中的病毒和细菌。

sentences.english: Mist eliminators remove drops of liquid from moving gas or vapor streams.
sentences.chinese: 除雾器可将流动气体或蒸汽中的液滴除去。
